data.description: This gorgeous home is located in a preferred beautiful subdivision in the area. There are mature trees and stately homes, located close to shopping, medical and cy-fair schools. The elegant entry greets your guest. There is a family room with a center fireplace, soaring ceilings and rich block paneling. The formal dining room also has a tall vaulted ceiling that follows the roofline. The island kitchen is spacious with an abundance of cabinet and counterspace. There is counterspace for chairs and an add  on area for a breakfast space. The garage in enclosed and finished out for an extra game room down. A Port Couchere for your cars. There is also a fantastic tool closet or space for storage. The primary is large and has a luxurious bath, there is a soaking tub and separate shower. There are also double sinks and plenty of counterspace. The primary closet is walk in, are most of the closets in the home. Upstairs there are 2 bedrooms, a bath and a game room. This home is priced to sell.
